irthday in       todd was my tour manager when i was on the road  we had a hit song with    because the night     and i bought it for him to symbolize everything we had to celebrate  all of these things  they   re memories  they all speak of someone     smith   s memoir m train is out in paperback on august        as told to thomas gebremedhin
